                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17841020-74-off340 t17841020-74-cd341"></join> last, a pair of girls leather shoes, value 3 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17841020-74-victim747" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
                     Dickson
                  <interp inst="t17841020-74-victim747" type="surname" value="Dickson"></interp>
